Dwarf Spell List (DC 18)
	CATEGORY:Special Ability
	TYPE:PathOfPowerChoice
	

#	DESC:"Five hundred years have I labored to produce this hammer; with it you shall smash giants as if they were mice."
#1 Magic Weapon: Weapon gains +1 bonus.
#2 Soften Earth and Stone: Turns stone to clay or dirt to sand or mud.
#3 Stone Shape: Sculpts stone into any shape.
#4 Stoneskin: Ignore 10 points of damage per attack.
#5 Wall of Stone: Creates a stone wall that can be shaped.
#6 Move Earth: Digs trenches and build hills.
#7 Wall of Iron: 30 hp/four levels; can topple onto foes.
#8 Iron Body: Your body becomes living iron.
#9 Mine Seed:* Plant a mine for the years to come.


Elf Spell List (DC 15)
	CATEGORY:Special Ability
	TYPE:PathOfPowerChoice
	

#	DESC:"You don't need to see my papers."
#1 Charm Person: Makes one person your friend.
#2 Fog Cloud: Fog obscures vision.
#3 Suggestion: Compels subject to follow stated course of action.
#4 Charm Monster: A monster believes it's your ally.
#5 Mind Fog: Subjects in fog get -10 to Wis and Will checks.
#6 Suggestion, Mass: As Suggestion, +1 subject/level.
#7 Power Word Blind: Blinds creature with 200 hp or less.
#8 Charm Monster, Mass: As charm monster, but all within 30 ft.
#9 Etherealness: Travel to Ethereal Plane with companions.




